defense secretary dick cheney held sensitive 
talks with saudi arabian officials monday about us military 
options for defending the oilrich desert kingdom against a 
possible blitzkrieg by iraqi forces massed along its border with 
kuwait 
the us aircraft carrier independence and its escort of a dozen 
warships and supply vessels reached the arabian sea putting the 
naval battle group close enough to launch air strikes against iraq 
and other targets in the persian gulf 
the independence joined the carrier eisenhower cruising in the 
