effect in 1994 and any money left in the fund at that time will 
revert to the guild 
also in the contract are new provisions for job security for 
noneditorial employees family leave and a new section on 
professional standards that covers such topics as libel suits and 
dealings with confidential sources 
the guild represents nearly 400 of the news 1100 employees 
