commodity exchange reflecting growing fears that the soaring price 
of crude oil will lead to higher inflation 
crude oil futures rose to their highest levels in more than 4 
years as iraq and the united states appeared to be headed for a 
showdown over iraqi aggression in the middle east 
on other commodity markets grain and soybean futures rose and 
livestock and meat futures were mixed 
