crude oil finished 1 to 356 higher with september at 2805 a 
barrel the highest settlement for a nearmonth crude oil contract 
since the latter half of 1985 heating oil futures settled 3 cents 
to 897 cents higher with september at 7555 cents a gallon 
unleaded gasoline was 3 cents to 934 cents higher with september 
at 8152 cents a gallon 
